{"tid":2245703,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特區政府：考慮暫不再推「空置稅」","createTime":"2020-10-16T12:15:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T12:17:23.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"79f1ac7b1b72b7f107eb9a32808fa7b91af185a9","tid":2245703,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:15:47.000Z","msg":"運輸及房屋局表示，因應最新的經濟情況、社會意見及早前相關法案委員會的意見，運房局正考慮，暫時不再推動對一手貨尾單位徵收額外差餉即「空置稅」和有關引進專營的士的工作。<br />\n<br />\n在今日下午的內會會議上，內會主席李慧琼引述運房局局長陳帆表示，局方考慮暫停專營的士及空置稅條例草案的審議，有待當局正式通知。"},{"pid":"ee0a880453e514556a842d7680a7fe52012c5d44","tid":2245703,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:15:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555173-20201016.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555173-20201016.htm&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVUwogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=fce985e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555173-20201016.htm&h=cfa8e237\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555173-20201016.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6625d36199c780340583483dd5c705069eab203b","tid":2245703,"uid":181789,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:17:08.000Z","msg":"你買埋我個份"},{"pid":"92081a2e1ea3d537a84dfca04d4927609fbc1a82","tid":2245703,"uid":180401,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:20:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痴線 走稅天堂"},{"pid":"f9b00286767a426184a4a50218aef63383cb1529","tid":2245703,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:20:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e0f04f2161dced4540f91d0a3ab86448636ad36","tid":2245703,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\